CSSDOC Bundle for TextMate
==========================

About
-----

This is a bundle for the [TextMate](http://macromates.com/) text editor. It gives you quick shortcuts for documenting your CSS projects.

You can learn more about CSSDOC at <http://cssdoc.net/>.

Installation
------------

- Install TextMate
- Download and double-click the CSSDOC.tmbundle
- Done!

